## 6. Success metrics for the rewrite

If built, measure against the current architecture on R7b's scope:

| Metric | Current (Fix #14+#15) | Target |
|---|---|---|
| LC-06 compliance | 100% | 100% (must not regress) |
| Solve time | ~22 min (full fleet) | ≤ 22 min (stretch: faster via parallel Stage A) |
| Model complexity | 5.7k assignments + inter-partition state | Stage A has cleaner model per partition; Stage B ~25k vars |
| Analyzer simplicity | Per-constraint analyzers + cross-partition aggregation | LC-06 analyzer sees full range naturally |
| Regression surface | Fix #14 + #15 + future proration fixes = 5 files of carryover-aware code | Single Stage B module; Stage A simpler |

